(AI)\n- `nextjs-app-router.mdx` (Web Dev)\n\n## Pending\n- GitLab group `maiy` creation\n- GitLab repo `maiy-tech-hub` creation\n- SSH key fix for git push\n- `yarn build` verification (installing now)\n- About page\n- Socket.IO server.ts\n- shadcn/ui component setup\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":109,"output":608,"cacheRead":100721,"cacheWrite":1847,"totalTokens":103285,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776570555479,"responseId":"063383bd5df69971839988f5d1bcbd8e"}}
