{"type":"message","id":"688b6454","parentId":"f2ffbd50","timestamp":"2026-04-19T04:02:14.129Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Both agents spawned successfully with DEV model. Let me also spawn a realistic-seeder agent to add more content. Then I'll wait for results.","thinkingSignature":"14671ab090c662b8eb0c8237457d7bc08326734d8f3fa7e8d54553484154191b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_q4wwphkgt314_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"You are realistic-seeder. Add 5 more MDX articles to the MAIY Tech Hub content folder.\n\nWORKSPACE: /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/\n\nTASK: Write 5 high-quality MDX articles covering different topics.\n\nWrite these files:\n\n1. content/articles/ctdl/dynamic-programming.mdx\n- Title: \"Dynamic Programming: Từ Fibonacci đến bài toán Balo\"\n- excerpt: \"DP là kỹ thuật tối ưu hóa bằng cách ghi nhớ kết quả. Mình sẽ giải thích DP qua 3 ví dụ cụ thể: Fibonacci, LCS, và bài toán Balo.\"\n- category: ctdl\n- tags: [\"dynamic-programming\", \"algorithm\", \"optimization\", \"knapsack\"]\n- hero: unsplash related to puzzle/logic\n- Include: recursive vs memoized vs tabulated approaches, LCS code, Knapsack code, when to use DP\n\n2. content/articles/ai/neural-network-from-scratch.mdx\n- Title: \"Neural Network từ scratch bằng NumPy: Không dùng thư viện ML\"\n- excerpt: \"Hiểu cách Neural Network hoạt động bằng cách implement từ đầu. Forward propagation, backpropagation, gradient descent — tất cả bằng NumPy.\"\n- category: ai\n- tags: [\"neural-network\", \"deep-learning\", \"numpy\", \"python\", \"scratch\"]\n- Include: Python code for a simple 2-layer network, sigmoid activation, MSE loss, gradient descent\n\n3. content/articles/web-dev/docker-compose.mdx\n- Title: \"Docker Compose: Deploy Full-Stack App trong 10 phút\"\n- excerpt: \"Docker không chỉ cho production. Mình sẽ hướng dẫn dùng Docker Compose để setup local dev environment cho Node.js + MongoDB + Redis.\"\n- category: web-dev\n- tags: [\"docker\", \"docker-compose\", \"devops\", \"mongodb\", \"nodejs\"]\n- Include: docker-compose.yml, Dockerfile for Node.js, explanation of volumes/networks\n\n4. content/articles/cs-fundamentals/stack-heap-memory.mdx\n- Title: \"Stack và Heap: Bộ nhớ hoạt động thế nào?\"\n- excerpt: \"Bạn đã bao giờ tự hỏi tại sao 'too much recursion' lại crash? Hay tại sao object được tạo bằng new() thì phải quản lý memory? Cùng mình tìm hiểu!\"\n- category: cs-fundamentals\n- tags: [\"memory\", \"stack\", \"heap\", \"pointers\", \"cs-fundamentals\"]\n- Include: Stack vs Heap comparison table, code examples in C/JS showing stack vs heap allocation\n\n5. content/articles/devops/github-actions-ci-cd.mdx\n- Title: \"GitHub Actions: Tự động test và deploy mỗi khi push\"\n- excerpt: \"Không cần Jenkins hay CircleCI. GitHub Actions là CI/CD miễn phí tích hợp sẵn. Mình sẽ hướng dẫn setup từ zero đến deploy lên Vercel.\"\n- category: devops\n- tags: [\"github-actions\", \"ci-cd\", \"devops\", \"github\", \"vercel\"]\n- Include: .github/workflows/ci.yml with test + lint steps, deployment step\n\nEach article should:\n- Be 600-1000 words\n- Have proper MDX frontmatter\n- Include code blocks with syntax hints\n- Use Vietnamese throughout\n- Have a concluding section with a teaser for next article\n\nUse the `write` tool for each file. Reply with a brief summary when done.","label":"maiy:realistic-seeder","runtime":"subagent","agentId":"realistic-seader","mode":"run"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":418,"output":979,"cacheRead":118301,"cacheWrite":2281,"totalTokens":121979,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776571310395,"responseId":"063386b0f2e2f9da17f5bb0113e9d2f4"}}
