{"type":"message","id":"92260a12","parentId":"e340d01a","timestamp":"2026-04-19T04:37:50.447Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Build is running. Let me also start spawning agents for the remaining phases while waiting for the build.","thinkingSignature":"fbd97bda9cf81c2e0a2df6a7bba6edcc1411230adc704a6a7acebd70d17a33d7"},{"type":"text","text":"Spawn Phase 4 agents trong lúc build:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_amoa1uxine6v_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"You are playwright-pro. Write E2E tests for MAIY Tech Hub.\n\nWORKSPACE: /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/\n\nTASK: Install Playwright and write E2E tests for all critical user flows.\n\nSTEPS:\n\n1. Install playwright:\n```\ncd /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub\nyarn add -D @playwright/test\nnpx playwright install chromium --with-deps\n```\n\n2. Create tests/e2e/ folder with these test files:\n\ntests/e2e/home.spec.ts:\n```typescript\nimport { test, expect } from '@playwright/test'\n\ntest.describe('Home Page', () => {\n  test('loads successfully', async ({ page }) => {\n    await page.goto('/')\n    await expect(page).toHaveTitle(/MAIY Tech Hub/)\n  })\n\n  test('shows hero section', async ({ page }) => {\n    await page.goto('/')\n    await expect(page.locator('h1')).toContainText('Kiến thức CNTT')\n  })\n\n  test('navigation links work', async ({ page }) => {\n    await page.goto('/')\n    await page.click('text=Bài viết')\n    await expect(page).toHaveURL(/\\/articles/)\n  })\n\n  test('dark mode toggle works', async ({ page }) => {\n    await page.goto('/')\n    const toggle = page.locator('[aria-label=\"Toggle theme\"]')\n    if (await toggle.isVisible()) {\n      await toggle.click()\n      await expect(page.locator('html')).toHaveClass(/dark/)\n    }\n  })\n})\n```\n\ntests/e2e/articles.spec.ts:\n```typescript\nimport { test, expect } from '@playwright/test'\n\ntest.describe('Articles', () => {\n  test('articles listing page loads', async ({ page }) => {\n    await page.goto('/articles')\n    await expect(page.locator('h1')).toContainText('bài viết')\n  })\n\n  test('article detail page loads', async ({ page }) => {\n    await page.goto('/articles/binary-search')\n    await expect(page.locator('h1')).toBeVisible()\n  })\n\n  test('category filter works', async ({ page }) => {\n    await page.goto('/articles')\n    const ctdlLink = page.locator('a[href*=\"/articles/category/ctdl\"]').first()\n    if (await ctdlLink.isVisible()) {\n      await ctdlLink.click()\n      await expect(page).toHaveURL(/\\/articles\\/category\\/ctdl/)\n    }\n  })\n})\n```\n\ntests/e2e/music.spec.ts:\n```typescript\nimport { test, expect } from '@playwright/test'\n\ntest.describe('Music Page', () => {\n  test('music page loads', async ({ page }) => {\n    await page.goto('/music')\n    await expect(page.locator('h1')).toContainText('Relaxation Zone')\n  })\n\n  test('mood selector changes playlist', async ({ page }) => {\n    await page.goto('/music')\n    const moodButtons = page.locator('button:has-text(\"Focus\"), button:has-text(\"Sleep\")')\n    const count = await moodButtons.count()\n    if (count > 0) {\n      await moodButtons.first().click()\n    }\n  })\n})\n```\n\ntests/e2e/study.spec.ts:\n```typescript\nimport { test, expect } from '@playwright/test'\n\ntest.describe('Study Page', () => {\n  test('study page loads', async ({ page }) => {\n    await page.goto('/study')\n    await expect(page.locator('h1')).toContainText('Phòng học')\n  })\n\n  test('create room button works', async ({ page }) => {\n    await page.goto('/study')\n    const createBtn = page.locator('button:has-text(\"Tạo phòng\")')\n    if (await createBtn.isVisible()) {\n      await createBtn.click()\n      await expect(page.locator('text=Phòng học:')).toBeVisible()\n    }\n  })\n})\n```\n\ntests/e2e/search.spec.ts:\n```typescript\nimport { test, expect } from '@playwright/test'\n\ntest.describe('Search', () => {\n  test('search page loads', async ({ page }) => {\n    await page.goto('/search')\n    await expect(page.locator('h1')).toContainText('Tìm kiếm')\n  })\n\n  test('search input is focusable', async ({ page }) => {\n    await page.goto('/search')\n    const input = page.locator('input[placeholder*=\"Tìm\"]')\n    await expect(input).toBeVisible()\n    await input.fill('binary search')\n  })\n})\n```\n\ntests/e2e/seo.spec.ts:\n```typescript\nimport { test, expect } from '@playwright/test'\n\ntest.describe('SEO', () => {\n  test('sitemap is accessible', async ({ page }) => {\n    const response = await page.goto('/sitemap.xml')\n    expect(response?.status()).toBe(200)\n  })\n\n  test('robots.txt is accessible', async ({ page }) => {\n    const response = await page.goto('/robots.txt')\n    expect(response?.status()).toBe(200)\n  })\n\n  test('article has OG tags', async ({ page }) => {\n    await page.goto('/articles/binary-search')\n    const ogTitle = page.locator('meta[property=\"og:title\"]')\n    await expect(ogTitle).toHaveAttribute('content', /.*/)\n  })\n})\n```\n\n3. Create playwright.config.ts:\n```typescript\nimport { defineConfig } from '@playwright/test'\n\nexport default defineConfig({\n  testDir: './tests/e2e',\n  fullyParallel: true,\n  forbidOnly: !!process.env.CI,\n  retries: process.env.CI ? 2 : 0,\n  workers: process.env.CI ? 1 : undefined,\n  reporter: 'html',\n  use: {\n    baseURL: 'http://localhost:3000',\n    trace: 'on-first-retry',\n  },\n  webServer: {\n    command: 'yarn dev',\n    url: 'http://localhost:3000',\n    reuseExistingServer: !process.env.CI,\n    timeout: 120000,\n  },\n})\n```\n\nWrite all files using `write` tool. Then run:\n```\ncd /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub\nyarn add -D @playwright/test\nnpx playwright install chromium\n```\n\nReply with summary when done.","label":"maiy:playwright-pro","runtime":"subagent","agentId":"playwright-pro","mode":"run"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_amoa1uxine6v_2","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"You are seo-audit. Perform a comprehensive SEO audit and fixes for MAIY Tech Hub.\n\nWORKSPACE: /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/\n\nTASK: Audit and implement missing SEO components.\n\nSTEPS:\n\n1. Create app/api/revalidate/route.ts:\n```typescript\nimport { NextResponse } from 'next/server'\nimport { revalidatePath, revalidateTag } from 'next/cache'\n\nexport async function POST(request: Request) {\n  const { searchParams } = new URL(request.url)\n  const secret = searchParams.get('secret')\n  const path = searchParams.get('path')\n\n  if (secret !== process.env.REVALIDATE_SECRET) {\n    return NextResponse.json({ message: 'Invalid secret' }, { status: 401 })\n  }\n\n  if (path) {\n    revalidatePath(path)\n    return NextResponse.json({ revalidated: true, path })\n  }\n\n  // Revalidate all article pages\n  revalidateTag('articles')\n  return NextResponse.json({ revalidated: true, message: 'All articles revalidated' })\n}\n```\n\n2. Create components/seo/web-site-schema.tsx:\n```typescript\nimport { SITE } from '@/config/site'\n\nexport function WebSiteSchema() {\n  const schema = {\n    '@context': 'https://schema.org',\n    '@type': 'WebSite',\n    name: SITE.name,\n    url: SITE.url,\n    description: SITE.description,\n    potentialAction: {\n      '@type': 'SearchAction',\n      target: {\n        '@type': 'EntryPoint',\n        urlTemplate: `${SITE.url}/search?q={search_term_string}`,\n      },\n      'query-input': 'required name=search_term_string',\n    },\n    publisher: {\n      '@type': 'Organization',\n      name: SITE.name,\n      url: SITE.url,\n    },\n  }\n  return (\n    <script\n      type=\"application/ld+json\"\n      dangerouslySetInnerHTML={{ __html: JSON.stringify(schema) }}\n    />\n  )\n}\n```\n\n3. Create components/seo/breadcrumb-schema.tsx:\n```typescript\nimport { SITE } from '@/config/site'\n\ninterface BreadcrumbItem {\n  label: string\n  href: string\n}\n\nexport function BreadcrumbSchema({ items }: { items: BreadcrumbItem[] }) {\n  const schema = {\n    '@context': 'https://schema.org',\n    '@type': 'BreadcrumbList',\n    itemListElement: [\n      {\n        '@type': 'ListItem',\n        position: 1,\n        name: 'Trang chủ',\n        item: SITE.url,\n      },\n      ...items.map((item, i) => ({\n        '@type': 'ListItem',\n        position: i + 2,\n        name: item.label,\n        item: `${SITE.url}${item.href}`,\n      })),\n    ],\n  }\n  return (\n    <script\n      type=\"application/ld+json\"\n      dangerouslySetInnerHTML={{ __html: JSON.stringify(schema) }}\n    />\n  )\n}\n```\n\n4. Update app/layout.tsx to include WebSiteSchema in the body:\n```typescript\n// Add inside body, before closing </body>:\n<WebSiteSchema />\n```\n\n5. Create app/about/page.tsx:\n```typescript\nimport { Metadata } from 'next'\nimport { Github, Mail, Heart } from 'lucide-react'\n\nexport const metadata: Metadata = {\n  title: 'Giới thiệu',\n  description: 'MAIY Tech Hub — Nền tảng blog chia sẻ kiến thức CNTT chuẩn chỉnh bằng tiếng Việt.',\n}\n\nexport default function AboutPage() {\n  return (\n    <div className=\"container py-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto\">\n      <h1 className=\"text-4xl font-bold mb-8\">Giới thiệu</h1>\n      \n      <div className=\"prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none\">\n        <h2>MAIY Tech Hub là gì?</h2>\n        <p>\n          MAIY Tech Hub là nền tảng blog chia sẻ kiến thức công nghệ thông tin \n          chuẩn chỉnh bằng tiếng Việt. Mỗi bài viết được viết cẩn thận với \n          code chạy được, giải thích dễ hiểu, và bài tập thực hành.\n        </p>\n\n        <h2>Tính năng</h2>\n        <ul>\n          <li>Bài viết chất lượng về CTDL, AI, Web Dev, DevOps</li>\n          <li>Khu vực âm nhạc thư giãn khi học</li>\n          <li>Phòng học live với Pomodoro timer</li>\n          <li>Tìm kiếm thông minh</li>\n          <li>Giao diện tối/sáng</li>\n        </ul>\n\n        <h2>Liên hệ</h2>\n        <p>\n          Đóng góp ý kiến hoặc đề xuất bài viết mới qua:\n        </p>\n        <ul>\n          <li>GitHub: <a href=\"https://github.com/khuowgn/maiy-tech-hub\">khuowgn/maiy-tech-hub</a></li>\n        </ul>\n\n        <p className=\"text-center text-muted-foreground mt-8\">\n          Kiến thức vì cộng đồng <Heart className=\"inline h-4 w-4 text-red-500\" />\n        </p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  )\n}\n```\n\n6. Add .env.example:\n```\nNEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=http://localhost:3000\nREVALIDATE_SECRET=your-secret-here\n```\n\nWrite all files. Reply with summary.","label":"maiy:seo-audit","runtime":"subagent","agentId":"seo-audit","mode":"run"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":108,"output":2876,"cacheRead":154523,"cacheWrite":289,"totalTokens":157796,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776573432714,"responseId":"06338efa2b864a59ebec7d7ae911c448"}}
