{"type":"message","id":"82364465","parentId":"f4a6ebe8","timestamp":"2026-04-19T04:52:51.012Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me add:\n1. PWA manifest2. Keyboard shortcut global listener (Cmd+K for search)\n3. More MDX articles (2 more)4. Better home page with featured categories5. FAQ page\n6. Contact page\n\nActually, let me focus on quality over quantity. Let me add:\n1. PWA manifest (manifest.json)\n2. Global keyboard shortcut listener (search)\n3. Better home page sections (stats, trending)\n4. A proper sitemap for search engines\n5. 2 more MDX articles\n6. Update globals.css with better typography","thinkingSignature":"d51334174308bd7d4ed74ec6baa267ce7b6bfe985af7c6f18fcf95d83864dcc6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lhj2lell6knl_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/public/manifest.json","content":"{\n  \"name\": \"MAIY Tech Hub\",\n  \"short_name\": \"MAIY\",\n  \"description\": \"Nền tảng blog chia sẻ kiến thức CNTT chuẩn chỉnh bằng tiếng Việt.\",\n  \"start_url\": \"/\",\n  \"display\": \"standalone\",\n  \"background_color\": \"#ffffff\",\n  \"theme_color\": \"#6366f1\",\n  \"icons\": [\n    {\n      \"src\": \"/icon-192.png\",\n      \"sizes\": \"192x192\",\n      \"type\": \"image/png\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"src\": \"/icon-512.png\",\n      \"sizes\": \"512x512\",\n      \"type\": \"image/png\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"categories\": [\"education\", \"technology\"],\n  \"lang\": \"vi\",\n  \"orientation\": \"portrait-primary\"\n}\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lhj2lell6knl_2","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/components/layout/keyboard-shortcut.tsx","content":"'use client'\n\nimport { useEffect } from 'react'\nimport { useRouter } from 'next/navigation'\n\nexport function KeyboardShortcuts() {\n  const router = useRouter()\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    const handler = (e: KeyboardEvent) => {\n      // Cmd/Ctrl + K → go to search\n      if ((e.metaKey || e.ctrlKey) && e.key === 'k') {\n        e.preventDefault()\n        router.push('/search')\n      }\n    }\n    document.addEventListener('keydown', handler)\n    return () => document.removeEventListener('keydown', handler)\n  }, [router])\n\n  return null\n}\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":89,"output":564,"cacheRead":74647,"cacheWrite":587,"totalTokens":75887,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776574363130,"responseId":"0633929c337e7b2fdd8e97599fded6b7"}}
