{"type":"message","id":"9386b137","parentId":"fe25db00","timestamp":"2026-04-19T04:59:45.590Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me check if the playwright agent has reported back. Also, let me update memory and then continue with more phases.\n\nLet me think about what else needs to be done to reach 90% completion:\n\n1. ✅ MDX rendering\n2. ✅ Reading progress bar\n3. ✅ Social share\n4. ✅ Table of contents\n5. ✅ Back to top\n6. ✅ Copy code button\n7. ✅ Newsletter form\n8. ✅ Loading skeletons\n9. ✅ 404 page\n10. ✅ Category pages\n11. ✅ Sort articles\n12. ✅ Search page with Fuse.js\n\n\n13. ✅ About page\n14. ✅ E2E tests\n15. ✅ SEO (schemas, sitemap, revalidation API)\n16. ✅ Lucide icons throughout\n17. ✅ Dark/light mode\n18. ✅ PWA manifest\n19. ✅ Keyboard shortcuts (Ctrl+K)\n20. ✅ Stats bar on home\n21. ✅ 10 MDX articles\n22. ✅ Responsive design\n23. ✅ Featured article on home\n24. ✅ Category badges\n25. ✅ Related articles on detail\n\nStill need to tackle the remaining 5% to hit 90%.\n\nI'm looking at what's left: a proper error boundary for catching React errors, setting up monitoring and analytics, integrating a comments system, adding a contributors or changelog page, and running performance audits to identify bottlenecks. Let me focus on the most impactful items.","thinkingSignature":"b2b1c26c6db20297b3522e0c3c71fd4a4406ea5bbce30473a36d747dccacee47"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pu063u7ycylc_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/app/error.tsx","content":"'use client'\n\nimport { useEffect } from 'react'\n\nexport default function Error({\n  error,\n  reset,\n}: {\n  error: Error & { digest?: string }\n  reset: () => void\n}) {\n  useEffect(() => {\n    // Log to error reporting service\n    console.error(error)\n  }, [error])\n\n  return (\n    <div className=\"container flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-[60vh] py-20 text-center\">\n      <div className=\"mb-6\">\n        <span className=\"text-6xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-rose-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent\">\n          Oops!\n        </span>\n      </div>\n      <h1 className=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-3\">Có lỗi xảy ra</h1>\n      <p className=\"text-muted-foreground mb-2 max-w-md\">\n        {error.message || 'Một lỗi không mong muốn đã xảy ra.'}\n      </p>\n      {error.digest && (\n        <p className=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground mb-8 font-mono\">\n          Error ID: {error.digest}\n        </p>\n      )}\n      <button\n        onClick={reset}\n        className=\"px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-primary text-primary-foreground font-medium hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors\"\n      >\n        Thử lại\n      </button>\n    </div>\n  )\n}\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pu063u7ycylc_2","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/app/changelog/page.tsx","content":"import { Metadata } from 'next'\nimport { Github, Heart } from 'lucide-react'\n\nexport const metadata: Metadata = {\n  title: 'Đóng góp',\n  description: 'Đóng góp bài viết cho MAIY Tech Hub - cùng xây dựng nền tảng kiến thức CNTT tiếng Việt.',\n}\n\nexport default function ContributePage() {\n  return (\n    <div className=\"container py-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto\">\n      <h1 className=\"text-4xl font-bold mb-8\">Đóng góp</h1>\n\n      <div className=\"prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8\">\n        <p className=\"text-lg text-muted-foreground\">\n          MAIY Tech Hub được xây dựng bởi cộng đồng. Mọi người đều có thể đóng góp bài viết!\n        </p>\n\n        <div className=\"not-prose grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8\">\n          <div className=\"rounded-xl border border-border p-6\">\n            <h3 className=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3\">Yêu cầu bài viết</h3>\n            <ul className=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">\n              <li className=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n                <span className=\"text-primary mt-1\">•</span>\n                Code phải chạy được, không chỉ lý thuyết\n              </li>\n              <li className=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n                <span className=\"text-primary mt-1\">•</span>\n                Giải thích rõ ràng, dễ hiểu cho người mới\n              </li>\n              <li className=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n                <span className=\"text-primary mt-1\">•</span>\n                Có ví dụ thực tế hoặc bài tập\n              </li>\n              <li className=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n                <span className=\"text-primary mt-1\">•</span>\n                Viết bằng tiếng Việt\n              </li>\n              <li className=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n                <span className=\"text-primary mt-1\">•</span>\n                Format MDX với frontmatter đầy đủ\n              </li>\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"rounded-xl border border-border p-6\">\n            <h3 className=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3\">Cách đóng góp</h3>\n            <ol className=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground list-decimal list-inside\">\n              <li>Fork repo trên GitHub</li>\n              <li>Thêm bài viết vào content/articles/</li>\n              <li>Viết bằng MDX với frontmatter</li>\n              <li>Tạo Pull Request</li>\n              <li>Chờ review và merge</li>\n            </ol>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <div className=\"rounded-xl border border-border p-6\">\n          <h3 className=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3\">Cấu trúc bài viết MDX</h3>\n          <pre className=\"bg-muted p-4 rounded-lg text-sm font-mono overflow-x-auto\">{`---\ntitle: \"Tiêu đề bài viết\"\nexcerpt: \"Mô tả ngắn gọn (1-2 câu)\"\ncategory: \"ctdl\"  # ctdl | ai | web-dev | devops | cs-fundamentals\ntags: [\"tag1\", \"tag2\", \"tag3\"]\nhero: \"https://images.unsplash.com/...\"\nauthor: \"Tên của bạn\"\ndate: \"2026-04-19\"\n---\n\n# Tiêu đề (H1)\n\n## Mục 2 (H2)\n\nCode example:\n\\`\\`\\`javascript\nconsole.log('Hello')\n\\`\\`\\``}</pre>\n        </div>\n\n        <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between rounded-xl border border-border p-6\">\n          <div>\n            <p className=\"font-semibold mb-1\">Xem source code</p>\n            <p className=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">\n              MAIY Tech Hub là open source\n            </p>\n          </div>\n          <a\n            href=\"https://github.com/khuowgn/maiy-tech-hub\"\n            target=\"_blank\"\n            rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\n            className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg bg-primary text-primary-foreground font-medium hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors\"\n          >\n            <Github className=\"h-4 w-4\" />\n            GitHub\n          </a>\n        </div>\n\n        <p className=\"text-center text-muted-foreground flex items-center justify-center gap-1\">\n          Kiến thức vì cộng đồng\n          <Heart className=\"h-4 w-4 text-red-500\" />\n        </p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  )\n}\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":401,"output":1931,"cacheRead":94032,"cacheWrite":412,"totalTokens":96776,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776574762184,"responseId":"0633942b1d311b022f89a9232bb297d2"}}
