{"type":"message","id":"e0ee1589","parentId":"d24e25f6","timestamp":"2026-04-19T05:01:02.310Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good - Playwright tests are there. Now let me also add a few more improvements to get to 90%:\n1. Add opengraph meta tags for social sharing\n2. Add a proper robots.ts \n3. Add RSS feed\n4. Make sure the mini-player handles state correctly\n\nActually, let me do a final quality check. The site has:- Home page with hero, stats, featured article, categories, recent posts, music/study previews, newsletter\n- Articles listing with sort- Article detail with TOC, reading progress, social share, related posts, copy code\n- Category pages- Music page with mood selector, YouTube embeds, mini-player\n\n\n- Study page with Pomodoro timer, room create/join, ambient sounds\n- Search page with Fuse.js\n- About page\n- Contribute page\n- 404 page\n- Loading skeletons\n- Error boundary\n- Dark/light mode\n- Lucide icons throughout\n- SEO (sitemap, robots, JSON-LD schemas, breadcrumbs, revalidation API)\n- PWA manifest\n- Keyboard shortcuts\n- 10 MDX articles\n- E2E tests\n\nThis is definitely above 90% completion. Let me do a final dev server restart and make sure everything is running.","thinkingSignature":"8d52f709ae90c23de303414a409346f1c879c4d91f0fe932f486a36277751120"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bzi9ya52y7dd_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"pkill -f \"next dev\" 2>/dev/null; sleep 1; cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub && yarn dev > /tmp/maiy-dev.log 2>&1 &\necho \"Dev restarted PID: $!\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":157,"output":356,"cacheRead":97109,"cacheWrite":371,"totalTokens":97993,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776574854620,"responseId":"063394871090b613ea1d964c8c23a97a"}}
