{"type":"message","id":"ed9e880a","parentId":"5886bebe","timestamp":"2026-04-19T05:04:55.978Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lead wants:\n1. Admin page for content management (publish, edit articles)\n2. More/better animations\n\nLet me plan this:\n\n**Admin Page:**\n- Login/auth (simple for now)\n- Dashboard with stats\n- Article management (CRUD)\n- Publish/unpublish articles\n- Category management\n- Music playlist management\n\n**Animations:**\n- Framer Motion already installed\n- Page transitions\n- Scroll animations (intersection observer)\n- Hover effects\n- Loading animations\n- Stagger animations\n\nLet me do both at once. I'll create a new branch `feat/admin-animations` and work on both.","thinkingSignature":"7dc5c52bd866b5ed1e27e4c8195e1827267db560c532dc6a76e24cb39e373796"},{"type":"text","text":"Rõ ràng! Admin page + animation improvements. Tạo branch mới và làm cả hai:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_779ojylb7vsc_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub && git checkout -b feat/admin-animations && echo \"On feat/admin-animations\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":771,"output":216,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":99233,"totalTokens":100220,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776575085172,"responseId":"0633956eca7ca71c787b55e47108b56b"}}
