{"type":"message","id":"3f4bbaff","parentId":"b3c0e578","timestamp":"2026-04-19T07:25:22.244Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Localhost returns 200 for the article. But Lead gets 404. Let me check what `generateStaticParams` returns - maybe the static pages aren't being found correctly.Wait, localhost returns 200 for /articles/binary-search, and the curl shows \"Binary Search\" title. But the lead gets 404. \n\nLet me think - the dev server might have cached the old version where getArticleBySlug returned null (because the recursive fix was just applied). The dev server should hot-reload but maybe there's a state issue.\n\nLet me check if the article is actually rendering content on localhost.","thinkingSignature":"447a969aee79d37301029126527c530b7c71ba4e5e3a9491eb1c3ab1e8011468"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gph4so55mkdq_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s http://localhost:3000/articles/binary-search 2>/dev/null | grep -o \"<title>[^<]*</title>\" && echo \"---\" && curl -s http://localhost:3000/articles/binary-search 2>/dev/null | grep -c \"code\\|MDX\\|Binary\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":79,"output":222,"cacheRead":162645,"cacheWrite":520,"totalTokens":163466,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776583514508,"responseId":"0633b65c1d0c3456fbe8b52b73252e83"}}
