{"type":"message","id":"811e4871","parentId":"1ee16e43","timestamp":"2026-04-19T07:25:49.032Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The tunnel returns 200 with the correct title. So the tunnel is also working. The 404 the lead was seeing was from before the fix.\n\nNow, Lead says he has a VPS and doesn't need the tunnel. The next step would be to deploy to his VPS. But first, let me make sure all article pages work:","thinkingSignature":"fe4e500d479ef438a4c9757b074926560d9f5c2fdda29f9678ef38ca4b52bc2e"},{"type":"text","text":"Tunnel đã fix rồi ✅ — trả về đúng article. Lỗi 404 trước đó là vì chưa có fix.\n\n**Link tunnel:** https://mechanisms-measures-your-britney.trycloudflare.com/articles/binary-search\n\nCòn nếu Lead muốn deploy lên **VPS riêng**, mình cần thông tin:\n\n1. **VPS IP** — để push code hoặc setup\n2. **SSH access** — username/key để deploy được\n3. **Domain** — có domain chưa, hay dùng IP tạm?\n\nTrước đó, mình có thể tạo Dockerfile để Lead build & deploy dễ dàng trên VPS:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_svo80h8771lf_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/Dockerfile","content":"FROM node:22-alpine AS deps\nWORKDIR /app\nCOPY package.json yarn.lock ./\nRUN yarn install --frozen-lockfile\n\nFROM node:22-alpine AS builder\nWORKDIR /app\nCOPY --from=deps /app/node_modules ./node_modules\nCOPY . .\nRUN yarn build\n\n# Production stage\nFROM node:22-alpine AS runner\nWORKDIR /app\n\nENV NODE_ENV=production\n\nRUN addgroup --system --gid 1001 nodejs\nRUN adduser --system --uid 1001 nextjs\n\nCOPY --from=builder /app/public ./public\nCOPY --from=builder /app/.next/standalone ./\nCOPY --from=builder /app/.next/static ./.next/static\n\nUSER nextjs\n\nEXPOSE 3000\n\nENV PORT=3000\nENV HOSTNAME=\"0.0.0.0\"\n\nCMD [\"node\", \"server.js\"]\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_svo80h8771lf_2","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/docker-compose.yml","content":"version: '3.8'\nservices:\n  maiy-tech-hub:\n    build: .\n    restart: always\n    ports:\n      - \"3000:3000\"\n    environment:\n      - NODE_ENV=production\n      - NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://your-domain.com\n      - ADMIN_PASSWORD=maiy2026\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":117,"output":606,"cacheRead":163177,"cacheWrite":590,"totalTokens":164490,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776583535269,"responseId":"0633b670f43b5151b85692f13022dd0e"}}
