{"type":"message","id":"04281189","parentId":"c65565e2","timestamp":"2026-04-19T07:27:33.212Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lead is saying they're working on a VPS and can access it through the VPS. They're saying I can work directly on the VPS. This means I should SSH into the VPS and deploy the project there directly.\n\nBut I need to know the VPS IP/hostname and SSH credentials. Let me ask... wait, maybe Lead is saying they already have access to the VPS and will provide the details. Or maybe they want me to set up the project on a VPS they have.\n\nActually, re-reading: \"Bạn đang là việc trong vps nên tôi có thể truy cập vào được qua vps\" — \"You're working in the VPS so I can access it through the VPS\"\n\n\nI think Lead is saying they're working on the VPS and want me to continue working directly there. They might be referring to the same machine I'm already on, so I should ask them to share the VPS details or confirm how they want me to proceed.\n\nActually, I realize I don't have the actual VPS connection information in my memory, so I need to ask Lead for the IP/hostname and SSH credentials so I can deploy MAIY Tech Hub to their server.","thinkingSignature":"a1de9ce041d2a38db4600a1b8cd0266603ab35837b66a7576401df6a8a1a695f"},{"type":"text","text":"Rõ rồi — Lead đang làm việc trên VPS. Để deploy lên VPS, mình cần thông tin SSH:\n\n**Cung cấp cho mình:**\n1. **VPS IP** (ví dụ: `103.x.x.x`)\n2. **SSH username** (thường là `root` hoặc `ubuntu`)\n3. **SSH key** — đã thêm public key vào VPS chưa, hay dùng password?\n\nNếu Lead muốn mình SSH vào và setup trực tiếp, cung cấp thông tin trên là được."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":388,"cacheRead":164802,"cacheWrite":912,"totalTokens":166102,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776583639749,"responseId":"0633b6d99fa61706e0ceca646e4113