{"type":"message","id":"7995b5e9","parentId":"e7ba148a","timestamp":"2026-04-19T07:37:16.131Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Queued messages while agent was busy]\n\n---\nQueued #1\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"4169\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"6053576134\",\n  \"sender\": \"Khương Nịnh\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-04-19 07:33 UTC\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Khương Nịnh (6053576134)\",\n  \"id\": \"6053576134\",\n  \"name\": \"Khương Nịnh\",\n  \"username\": \"khuowgn\"\n}\n```\n\nTiếp theo giúp tôi làm tính năng trong phòng học, bật cam, nói chuyện, chat, mở nhan"}],"timestamp":1776584236093}}
{"type":"message","id":"59aa1b43","parentId":"7995b5e9","timestamp":"2026-04-19T07:37:42.358Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to continue building the study room features: camera, voice chat, chat, screen share. Let me continue building the components. I already created the WebRTC library and ChatPanel. Now I need to create:\n\n1. Video grid component\n2. Controls component\n3. Media permissions hook\n4. Update the study page to integrate everything\n\nLet me continue building all of these.","thinkingSignature":"a461f2eb86ea6553b4e1e861d824d9b45d3304ab5e213b1795f028ec6bb775ab"},{"type":"text","text":"\nĐang tiếp tục build! Video grid + Controls:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ltn7aq18gcra_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/components/study/video-grid.tsx","content":"'use client'\n\nimport { useRef, useEffect } from 'react'\nimport { User, Mic, MicOff, VideoOff } from 'lucide-react'\nimport { motion } from 'framer-motion'\n\nexport interface VideoPeer {\n  peerId: string\n  peerName: string\n  stream: MediaStream\n  isMuted?: boolean\n  isVideoOff?: boolean\n  isScreenSharing?: boolean\n}\n\ninterface VideoTileProps {\n  peer: VideoPeer\n  isLocal?: boolean\n  isMain?: boolean\n  onClick?: () => void\n}\n\nfunction VideoTile({ peer, isLocal, isMain, onClick }: VideoTileProps) {\n  const videoRef = useRef<HTMLVideoElement>(null)\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    if (videoRef.current && peer.stream) {\n      videoRef.current.srcObject = peer.stream\n    }\n  }, [peer.stream])\n\n  const hasVideo = peer.stream?.getVideoTracks().some((t) => t.enabled && !peer.isVideoOff)\n  const hasAudio = peer.stream?.getAudioTracks().some((t) => t.enabled && !peer.isMuted)\n\n  return (\n    <motion.div\n      whileHover={{ scale: 1.02 }}\n      onClick={onClick}\n      className={`relative rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-slate-900 border-2 border-border\n        ${isMain ? 'aspect-video' : 'aspect-video'}\n        ${peer.isScreenSharing ? 'ring-2 ring-primary' : ''}`}\n    >\n      {/* Video / Avatar */}\n      {hasVideo ? (\n        <video\n          ref={videoRef}\n          autoPlay\n          playsInline\n          muted={isLocal}\n          className={`w-full h-full object-cover ${isLocal ? 'scale-x-[-1]' : ''}`}\n        />\n      ) : (\n        <div className=\"w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center\">\n          <div className=\"w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-primary/20 flex items-center justify-center\">\n            <User className=\"h-8 w-8 text-primary\" />\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      )}\n\n      {/* Name tag */}\n      <div className=\"absolute bottom-2 left-2 right-2 flex items-center justify-between\">\n        <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-black/60 backdrop-blur-sm px-2 py-1 rounded-full\">\n          {!hasAudio && <MicOff className=\"h-3 w-3 text-red-400\" />}\n          <span className=\"text-white text-xs font-medium\">\n            {isLocal ? 'Bạn' : peer.peerName}\n          </span>\n        </div>\n        {peer.isScreenSharing && (\n          <span className=\"bg-primary/90 text-primary-foreground text-[10px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-medium\">\n            Đang chia sẻ màn hình\n          </span>\n        )}\n      </div>\n\n      {/* Audio indicator */}\n      {hasAudio && !isLocal && (\n        <div className=\"absolute top-2 right-2\">\n          <div className=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-400 animate-pulse\" />\n        </div>\n      )}\n\n      {/* Screen share overlay */}\n      {peer.isScreenSharing && (\n        <div className=\"absolute top-2 left-2\">\n          <div className=\"bg-primary/90 text-primary-foreground text-[10px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full font-medium flex items-center gap-1\">\n            <span className=\"w-2 h-2 bg-primary-foreground rounded-full\" />\n            Screen\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      )}\n    </motion.div>\n  )\n}\n\ninterface VideoGridProps {\n  localStream: MediaStream | null\n  peers: VideoPeer[]\n  mainPeerId?: string\n  onSelectPeer?: (peerId: string) => void\n}\n\nexport function VideoGrid({ localStream, peers, mainPeerId, onSelectPeer }: VideoGridProps) {\n  const localVideoRef = useRef<HTMLVideoElement>(null)\n\n  useEffect(() => {\n    if (localVideoRef.current && localStream) {\n      localVideoRef.current.srcObject = localStream\n    }\n  }, [localStream])\n\n  const totalVideos = peers.length + (localStream ? 1 : 0)\n\n  // Grid layout: 1=1, 2=2col, 3-4=2x2, 5-6=3col, 7+=4col\n  const getGridClass = () => {\n    if (totalVideos === 1) return 'grid-cols-1 max-w-md mx-auto'\n    if (totalVideos === 2) return 'grid-cols-2'\n    if (totalVideos <= 4) return 'grid-cols-2'\n    if (totalVideos <= 6) return 'grid-cols-3'\n    return 'grid-cols-4'\n  }\n\n  return (\n    <div className={`grid ${getGridClass()} gap-3 p-4`}>\n      {/* Local video */}\n      {localStream && (\n        <VideoTile\n          peer={{\n            peerId: 'local',\n            peerName: 'Bạn',\n            stream: localStream,\n          }}\n          isLocal\n          isMain={!mainPeerId}\n          onClick={() => onSelectPeer?.('local')}\n        />\n      )}\n\n      {/* Remote peers */}\n      {peers.map((peer) => (\n        <VideoTile\n          key={peer.peerId}\n          peer={peer}\n          isMain={peer.peerId === mainPeerId}\n          onClick={() => onSelectPeer?.(peer.peerId)}\n        />\n      ))}\n\n      {/* Empty slots */}\n      {totalVideos === 0 && (\n        <div className=\"col-span-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center py-20 text-center\">\n          <div className=\"w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-muted flex items-center justify-center mb-4\">\n            <User className=\"h-10 w-10 text-muted-foreground\" />\n          </div>\n          <p className=\"text-muted-foreground\">Bật camera để bắt đầu</p>\n        </div>\n      )}\n    </div>\n  )\n}\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":0,"output":1516,"cacheRead":18298,"cacheWrite":26645,"totalTokens":46459,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776584236132,"responseId":"0633b92d0fef4a1ab2c09ef5d7ba39e4"}}
