{"type":"message","id":"0a4d3d55","parentId":"bae45904","timestamp":"2026-04-19T08:03:06.381Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Server is up. The Study Room v2 WebRTC signaling has been rewritten.\n\nKey improvements:\n1. Each WebSocket connection gets a unique `peerId` from the server\n2. When a peer joins, they get a `welcome` message with all existing peers\n3. The new peer creates offers to all existing peers (mesh topology)\n4. Existing peers are notified and create offers to the new peer\n5. ICE candidates, offers, answers are relayed correctly\n6. Better error handling and reconnection\n\nThe remaining limitation: WebRTC on the same network (same VPS) should work fine. For peers on different networks, STUN servers should help. For truly unreachable peers (symmetric NAT), TURN servers would be needed (which are not free).\n\n\nThis should work well for the Lead's use case on the VPS network. Now I'll explain this clearly to the Lead.","thinkingSignature":"354a438dcf590658e8a26973a877970bb73a6b6cf8acc29336a3b9a664ecb0b0"},{"type":"text","text":"Server ✅ — WebRTC signaling đã viết lại hoàn toàn.\n\n**Đã fix:**\n- Mỗi user được gán `peerId` duy nhất từ server\n- Khi join: nhận danh sách peers hiện có → tự tạo offer đến tất cả\n- ICE candidates / offer / answer được relay đúng peer\n- Tự reconnect khi mất kết nối\n\n**Cách test:**\n1. Mở 2 tab trình duyệt (hoặc 2 máy khác nhau)\n2. Tab 1: http://103.253.21.139:3000/study → nhập tên → `#CTDL`\n3. Tab 2: http://103.253.21.139:3000/study → nhập tên → `CTDL` (cùng mã phòng)\n4. Cả 2 sẽ kết nối peer-to-peer qua WebRTC\n\n**Lưu ý:** Camera/mic cần HTTPS hoặc localhost để hoạt động. Nếu truy cập qua `http://`, trình duyệt sẽ chặn camera/mic. Lead nên dùng HTTPS hoặc test trên localhost.\n\nĐể bật HTTPS tạm thời, có thể dùng Cloudflare tunnel đã setup ở trên:\n**https://mechanisms-measures-your-britney.trycloudflare.com/study**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":110,"output":535,"cacheRead":74408,"cacheWrite":181,"totalTokens":75234,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776585771508,"responseId":"0633bf2d34af8328a7876b5a24daea5c"}}
