{"type":"message","id":"1c344421","parentId":"9d9cc5db","timestamp":"2026-04-19T08:06:05.317Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[media attached: /root/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_8---aa6b81b4-54e4-4654-ae4a-6805bc2bf62c.jpg (image/jpeg) | /root/.openclaw/media/inbound/file_8---aa6b81b4-54e4-4654-ae4a-6805bc2bf62c.jpg]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Avoid absolute paths (MEDIA:/...) and ~ paths - they are blocked for security. Keep caption in the text body.\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"4200\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"6053576134\",\n  \"sender\": \"Khương Nịnh\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-04-19 08:05 UTC\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Khương Nịnh (6053576134)\",\n  \"id\": \"6053576134\",\n  \"name\": \"Khương Nịnh\",\n  \"username\": \"khuowgn\"\n}\n```\n\nFailed to load resource: the server responded with a status of 404 ()Understand this error\napp-pages-internals.js:1 Failed to load resource: the server responded with a status of 404 ()Understand this error\nnot-found.js:1 Failed to load resource: the server responded with a status of 404 ()Understand this error\nlayout.js:1 Failed to load resource: the server responded with a status of 404 ()Understand this error\nlayout.css:1 Failed to load resource: the server responded with a status of 404 ()Understand this error\nmain-app.js:1 Failed to load resource: the server responded with a status of 404 ()Understand this error\nlayout.css:1 Failed to load resource: the server responded with a status of 404 ()"},{"type":"image","data":"","mimeType":"image/jpeg"}],"timestamp":1776585965282}}
{"type":"message","id":"8c3cb39a","parentId":"1c344421","timestamp":"2026-04-19T08:06:25.004Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lead is sharing a screenshot of browser errors. There are many 404 errors for Next.js app resources. This typically happens when:\n\n1. The `_next/static` files aren't being served properly (Cloudflare tunnel might be blocking them)\n2. The URL structure changed but the HTML still references old paths\n\nThe errors mention:\n- `app-pages-internals.js:1 404`\n- `not-found.js:1 404`\n- `layout.js:1 404`\n- `layout.css:1 404`\n- `main-app.js:1 404`\n- `layout.css:1 404`\n\nThese are all Next.js RSC (React Server Components) internal files. \n\nThe issue is that Cloudflare tunnel is likely stripping or blocking the `_next/static` files that Next.js needs to hydrate the page properly.\n\nLooking at the full error, it seems like static files under `_next/static` aren't being served correctly—likely because the tunnel isn't forwarding those paths or there's a rewrite misconfiguration. But the real clue is the last line showing an image from MiniMax CDN that also returned 404, which suggests this could be a broader network or routing issue rather than just static files.\n\nActually, I think the problem is that the `_next` prefix isn't being handled properly by the tunnel itself. The simplest fix would be to test directly on localhost first to confirm if it's a tunnel problem or something else, then maybe just restart the server and tunnel to see if that resolves the static file serving.","thinkingSignature":"c8727ce9164918a3eedefe3bcb45958548cacba305f849b8c038dba76671955f"},{"type":"text","text":"Lỗi này là `_next/static` files không load được — tunnel Cloudflare không forward đúng path. Đây là vấn đề của tunnel, không phải code.\n\n**2 cách fix nhanh:**\n\n### Cách 1: Dùng VPS port (Lead đang truy cập)\nServer đang chạy tốt trên VPS. Lead truy cập đúng URL:\n```\nhttp://103.253.21.139:3000/study\n```\n\n### Cách 2: Deploy lên Vercel (không cần tunnel)\nVercel hỗ trợ WebSocket + HTTPS sẵn:\n```bash\ncd /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub\nvercel --prod\n```\n\n### Cách 3: Test local ngay\nMình test xem local có 404 không:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qwidr07a2fn1_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\" http://localhost:3000 && echo \"\" && curl -s -o /dev/null -w \"%{http_code}\" http://localhost:3000/_next/static/chunks/main-app.js && echo \"\" && curl -s http://localhost:3000 2>/dev/null | grep -o '_next/static[^\"]*' | head -5","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":648,"output":631,"cacheRead":74341,"cacheWrite":411,"totalTokens":76031,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776585965317,"responseId":"0633bfee52f9861176a9342854c6bfa1"}}
