{"type":"message","id":"64fa9ec7","parentId":"9ccf69d6","timestamp":"2026-04-19T08:08:43.322Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, vercel is installed. Now let me try to deploy. But I need authentication. Let me check if there's already a vercel config or login session.\n\nActually, let me think about this differently. The real issue is the dev server not serving static files correctly. Let me fix this by running in production mode instead, and serve with a proper server.\n\nOr better yet - let me update the vercel.json and push to GitLab, then use Vercel's GitHub/GitLab integration to deploy. But the repo is on GitLab, not GitHub.\n\nActually, the simplest approach for now:\n1. Update `package.json` scripts to use `next start` (production)\n\n\n2. Build the production version\n3. Serve with `next start`\n\nIn production mode, Next.js handles static files correctly. Let me do this first, then also set up Vercel deployment for long-term HTTPS.\n\nActually, the real blocker here is that camera and microphone won't work without HTTPS on the VPS. The 404 errors are likely a separate issue. Let me focus on the core problem: getting HTTPS working so WebRTC can function properly.\n\nFor HTTPS on the VPS, I'd need a domain pointed to the server, then I can set up Nginx with Let's Encrypt. Since that might take setup time, deploying to Vercel is the faster path—I'll create a vercel.json config and push it to the repo so Lead can deploy directly from there.","thinkingSignature":"eee7f1e81137c9508ca233df80acac03fe925f6a0aabd3b52beb562ca4df98d1"},{"type":"text","text":"Vercel CLI đã cài. Để nhanh nhất, mình tạo config + deploy:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_onktpr4u9c9d_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/vercel.json","content":"{\n  \"framework\": \"nextjs\",\n  \"buildCommand\": \"yarn build\",\n  \"devCommand\": \"yarn dev\",\n  \"installCommand\": \"yarn install\",\n  \"regions\": [\"sin1\"],\n  \"functions\": {\n    \"app/api/**/*.ts\": {\n      \"memory\": 512,\n      \"maxDuration\": 10\n    }\n  }\n}\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":83,"output":457,"cacheRead":78321,"cacheWrite":439,"totalTokens":79300,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776586112082,"responseId":"0633c081a009eed3560e8a0aba6761c1"}}
