{"type":"message","id":"5966be32","parentId":"0facfab4","timestamp":"2026-04-19T08:22:26.978Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ghrrrmz5kev5_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-04-19 — Orbis Daily Log\n\n## 03:25 UTC — Session Start\n- Lead connected via Telegram direct\n- Ecosystem: 34 agents, v4-ecosystem-review repo\n- DTLX BE/FE: last known running ports 5555/3000 (need verification)\n\n## 03:28 UTC — New Project Kickoff: AHV Tech Knowledge Hub\n\n### Requirements (from Lead)\nBuild a blog sharing IT/CS knowledge (CTDL & GT, AI, etc.) + music relaxation + live study room.\n- Must be beautiful and modern\n- Quality, well-structured content\n- Proper SEO\n\n### OpenSpec Created\n- Location: `ahv-knowledge-hub/openspec/changes/tech-blog/`\n- Files: `proposal.md` + `tasks.md`\n- Tasks: 35 tasks across 8 phases\n\n### Phase 1 Agents Launched (parallel)\n| Agent | Task | Status |\n|-------|------|--------|\n| senior-architect | System architecture (Next.js structure, data flow) | 🚀 Spawning |\n| content-strategy | Content pillars for CTDL, AI, CS Fundamentals | 🚀 Spawning |\n| ai-seo | SEO strategy + structured data schema | 🚀 Spawning |\n| ui-ux-pro-max | Wireframes for all 5 core pages | 🚀 Spawning |\n| stitch-design | High-fidelity visual mockups | ⏳ After T3 |\n| product-marketing-context | Brand voice, ICP | 🚀 Spawning |\n\n### Tech Stack Decided\n- **Frontend:** Next.js 14 (App Router) + TypeScript + Tailwind + shadcn/ui\n- **Animation:** Framer Motion\n- **Content:** MDX (local files)\n- **Music:** YouTube/Spotify embed\n- **Live Study:** Socket.IO on same Next.js server\n- **SEO:** next-sitemap + next-seo + JSON-LD\n- **Hosting:** Vercel\n\n### Next Steps After Phase 1\n- T8: senior-frontend scaffolds Next.js project\n- All implementation phases follow SDLC\n\n## Blockers\n- GitLab repo not yet created for `ahv-knowledge-hub`\n- Git SSH key issue (Permission denied on git fetch)\n\n## 03:42 UTC — Project Renamed + Phase 2 Scaffold\n- Lead confirmed: rename to \"MAIY Tech Hub\" ✅\n- Model check: agents already using TroLy (correct), 500 errors = provider issue\n- GitLab group `maiy` needs manual creation by Lead\n- Phase 2: scaffolded full Next.js 14 project\n- Build: passed ✅ | Lint: no warnings ✅\n- Commit: 6e16616 (44 files, 9494 lines)\n- Push: pending (SSH key + repo doesn't exist)\n\n## GitLab Setup (Lead cần làm)\n1. Tạo group `maiy` trên GitLab\n2. Tạo repo `maiy-tech-hub` trong group `maiy`\n3. Add SSH key lên GitLab\n4. Push code lên repo mới\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776586946975}}
{"type":"message","id":"c2917e72","parentId":"5966be32","timestamp":"2026-04-19T08:22:47.927Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to append new memories to this file, not overwrite it. Let me add the new content from today's session.","thinkingSignature":"fb741d25d4aa7359589cd254b028d5a642d1f7b9aa0e3b7696ddb7b33bb11ced"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_vbfe54vqaaop_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/2026-04-19.md","content":"# 2026-04-19 — Orbis Daily Log\n\n## 03:25 UTC — Session Start\n- Lead connected via Telegram direct\n- Ecosystem: 34 agents, v4-ecosystem-review repo\n- DTLX BE/FE: last known running ports 5555/3000 (need verification)\n\n## 03:28 UTC — New Project Kickoff: AHV Tech Knowledge Hub\n\n### Requirements (from Lead)\nBuild a blog sharing IT/CS knowledge (CTDL & GT, AI, etc.) + music relaxation + live study room.\n- Must be beautiful and modern\n- Quality, well-structured content\n- Proper SEO\n\n### OpenSpec Created\n- Location: `ahv-knowledge-hub/openspec/changes/tech-blog/`\n- Files: `proposal.md` + `tasks.md`\n- Tasks: 35 tasks across 8 phases\n\n### Phase 1 Agents Launched (parallel)\n| Agent | Task | Status |\n|-------|------|--------|\n| senior-architect | System architecture (Next.js structure, data flow) | 🚀 Spawning |\n| content-strategy | Content pillars for CTDL, AI, CS Fundamentals | 🚀 Spawning |\n| ai-seo | SEO strategy + structured data schema | 🚀 Spawning |\n| ui-ux-pro-max | Wireframes for all 5 core pages | 🚀 Spawning |\n| stitch-design | High-fidelity visual mockups | ⏳ After T3 |\n| product-marketing-context | Brand voice, ICP | 🚀 Spawning |\n\n### Tech Stack Decided\n- **Frontend:** Next.js 14 (App Router) + TypeScript + Tailwind + shadcn/ui\n- **Animation:** Framer Motion\n- **Content:** MDX (local files)\n- **Music:** YouTube/Spotify embed\n- **Live Study:** Socket.IO on same Next.js server\n- **SEO:** next-sitemap + next-seo + JSON-LD\n- **Hosting:** Vercel\n\n### Next Steps After Phase 1\n- T8: senior-frontend scaffolds Next.js project\n- All implementation phases follow SDLC\n\n## Blockers\n- GitLab repo not yet created for `ahv-knowledge-hub`\n- Git SSH key issue (Permission denied on git fetch)\n\n## 03:42 UTC — Project Renamed + Phase 2 Scaffold\n- Lead confirmed: rename to \"MAIY Tech Hub\" ✅\n- Model check: agents already using TroLy (correct), 500 errors = provider issue\n- GitLab group `maiy` needs manual creation by Lead\n- Phase 2: scaffolded full Next.js 14 project\n- Build: passed ✅ | Lint: no warnings ✅\n- Commit: 6e16616 (44 files, 9494 lines)\n- Push: pending (SSH key + repo doesn't exist)\n\n## GitLab Setup (Lead cần làm)\n1. Tạo group `maiy` trên GitLab\n2. Tạo repo `maiy-tech-hub` trong group `maiy`\n3. Add SSH key lên GitLab\n4. Push code lên repo mới\n\n## 07:14 UTC — MAIY Tech Hub Active Development\n\n### Project Status: 100% Feature Complete (Build 42/42 pages)\n**Repo:** https://gitlab.com/maiy-hub/maiy-tech-hub\n**Workspace:** /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/\n**Dev Server:** http://103.253.21.139:3000 (port 3000)\n**HTTPS Tunnel:** https://efficient-bell-parameter-locate.trycloudflare.com\n\n### Bugs Fixed Today\n1. **404 articles** — `getArticleFiles()` chỉ đọc root dir, không subdirs. Đã fix recursive walk.\n2. **Slug bug** — slug chứa `web-dev/` prefix từ subdirectory. Đã strip subdirectory prefix.\n3. **Next.js static build** — pages không pre-render đúng vì slug mismatch. Đã fix 42/42.\n\n### Study Room v2 — WebRTC Features Added\n- Camera on/off (getUserMedia)\n- Microphone on/off\n- Screen sharing (getDisplayMedia)\n- Real-time chat (PeerJS data channels)\n- Video grid (auto-layout 1→N)\n- Room codes for join/create\n- Quick join: #CTDL, #AI, #WebDev\n\n### Tech Stack Changes\n- **Signaling:** PeerJS (0.peerjs.com cloud server) — no custom server needed for WebRTC\n- **Dockerfile** + **docker-compose.yml** created for VPS deployment\n- **vercel.json** created for Vercel deployment\n- Output mode: `standalone` in next.config.mjs\n\n### Key Files\n- `components/study/study-room.tsx` — main room component (PeerJS + WebRTC)\n- `components/study/video-grid.tsx` — video tile grid\n- `components/study/media-controls.tsx` — control bar (mic/cam/screen/chat/leave)\n- `components/study/chat-panel.tsx` — chat sidebar\n- `lib/webrtc.ts` — WebRTC utilities\n- `server/server.ts` — custom Next.js server (Socket.IO + native WS)\n\n### VPS Deployment Info\n- VPS IP: 103.253.21.139\n- Dev server running on port 3000\n- Cloudflare tunnel available for HTTPS testing\n- Dockerfile ready: `docker build -t maiy-hub . && docker run -p 3000:3000 maiy-hub`\n\n### Known Issues\n- WebRTC camera/mic requires HTTPS or localhost (browser permission)\n- Tunnel Cloudflare may die — restart with: `cloudflared tunnel --url http://localhost:3000`\n- Dev server PID changes on restart — check with `pgrep -f \"next dev\"`\n\n### Git Workflow\n- All work on `feat/100-percent` branch\n- Feature branches merged to develop (self-merge approved by Lead)\n- Current HEAD: develop (after multiple feat merges)\n- Admin password: `maiy2026` (ADMIN_PASSWORD env var)\n\n### Remaining TODO\n- Real-time collaboration study rooms (needs STUN/TURN server for production)\n- Comments system (needs backend/DB)\n- Analytics integration (Vercel Analytics)\n- Production deployment (VPS or Vercel)\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":676,"output":1449,"cacheRead":54650,"cacheWrite":283,"totalTokens":57058,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776586946986,"responseId":"0633c3c407f72ed684af3c4cdb2e2b67"}}
