{"type":"message","id":"d710255b","parentId":"2c15ea72","timestamp":"2026-04-19T08:36:01.013Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me also check and fix the slow page navigation. The issue might be that the custom server isn't pre-rendering pages efficiently. Let me also add `yarn dev` to check if the issue is with the custom server vs the dev server.Actually, the most impactful thing for page load performance is to make sure pages are statically generated. Since I added `export const dynamic = 'force-static'`, the article pages should be pre-rendered. But the `tsx server/server.ts` running in dev mode might still be slow.Let me check if using `next start` (production mode) is faster. But since we're using a custom server, we can't use `next start` directly.Let me think about the navigation issue differently. When the user clicks from \"Bài viết\" to \"Âm nhạc\", what's happening:1. Next.js client-side navigation triggers2. The new page fetches its data3. The page rendersThe slowness could be:1. The music page takes too long to render\n\n\n2. Or there's a hydration mismatch causing a flash\n\nThe music page likely isn't statically generated, so it's rendering on-demand with server-side processing. I should make sure the music page has static generation configured so it pre-renders during the build and loads instantly.\n\nLooking at what the music page does—it probably loads YouTube embeds or fetches data—that could be causing the delay. I'll use ISR to regenerate it periodically instead of regenerating on every request. But first, let me focus on the copy buttons fix and test the current setup before diving into optimization.\n\nActually, the real issue is likely that the dev server is compiling MDX with rehype-highlight on every request, which is slow. Switching to a production build would cache the compiled pages and be much faster. Since the build is already done, I should restart the server with the new compiled version.","thinkingSignature":"f5d8777a783165e47f9f2a7d87253be454df71f1bcd6c9f4496dc017d053290b"},{"type":"text","text":"Build xong ✅. Commit & deploy:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2rddzzablp37_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub && git add . && git commit -m \"fix(maiy): syntax highlighting with highlight.js GitHub Dark + copy buttons\n\n- highlight.js with github-dark theme for code blocks\n- rehype-highlight as MDX plugin (server-side)\n- Copy button on every code block with language label\n- Code styling: dark bg, border, rounded\n- Build: 42/42 pages ✅\" 2>&1 | tail -3","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":113,"output":541,"cacheRead":115388,"cacheWrite":1216,"totalTokens":117258,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776587745528,"responseId":"0633c6e37410da8fc6206948990a2b96"}}
