{"type":"message","id":"5998de7a","parentId":"0b10a010","timestamp":"2026-04-19T09:16:50.916Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me plan the redesign. Based on the screenshot analysis, I need to:\n\n1. **Category pills** — make them more modern with:\n   - Gradient backgrounds for active state\n   - Better hover states\n   - Consistent language (all Vietnamese)\n   - Active indicator with gradient underline\n\n2. **Article cards** — modernize with:\n   - Gradient borders on hover\n   - Better typography\n   - Cleaner layout\n   - Better spacing\n\n3. **Overall** — add:\n   - More modern component library\n   - Better shadows and glows\n   - Premium feel\n   - Consistent spacing system\n   - Better animations\n\nLet me focus on the key areas:\n1. Category navigation\n2. Article cards\n3. Featured section\n4. Home page layout\n5. Better CSS system\n\nLet me start with the category pills since that's the main visible element, then work on article cards and other sections.","thinkingSignature":"748364118a10c28bfc837862b07a1c84a38ac945eefc4c21761b7ff1cf58281e"},{"type":"text","text":"Branch `feat/redesign` đã tạo. Bắt đầu redesign hệ thống:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_a3git8hhcgx3_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/app/page.tsx","limit":80}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":111,"output":274,"cacheRead":140424,"cacheWrite":1634,"totalTokens":142443,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776590202071,"responseId":"0633d07be2891a9bb5b913bd423aca99"}}
{"type":"message","id":"4ddbd3be","parentId":"5998de7a","timestamp":"2026-04-19T09:16:50.967Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_a3git8hhcgx3_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import Link from 'next/link'\nimport { ArrowRight, Play, Headphones, BookOpen } from 'lucide-react'\nimport { CATEGORIES } from '@/config/site'\nimport { ArticleCard } from '@/components/blog/article-card'\nimport { NewsletterForm } from '@/components/shared/newsletter-form'\nimport { ThreeHero } from '@/components/blog/three-hero'\nimport { getFeaturedArticles, getRecentArticles } from '@/lib/content'\n\nexport default async function HomePage() {\n  const featured = await getFeaturedArticles()\n  const recent = await getRecentArticles(6)\n  const featuredArticle = featured[0]\n\n  return (\n    <div className=\"flex flex-col\">\n      <ThreeHero />\n\n      {/* Featured Article */}\n      {featuredArticle && (\n        <section className=\"container py-12\">\n          <h2 className=\"text-sm font-semibold text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wider mb-6\">\n            Bài viết nổi bật\n          </h2>\n          <Link\n            href={`/articles/${featuredArticle.slug}`}\n            className=\"group block rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-border/40 hover:border-primary/30 transition-all hover:shadow-lg\"\n          >\n            <div className=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-0\">\n              {featuredArticle.hero && (\n                // eslint-disable-next-line @next/next/no-img-element\n                <img\n                  src={featuredArticle.hero}\n                  alt={featuredArticle.title}\n                  className=\"w-full h-64 md:h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500\"\n                />\n              )}\n              <div className=\"p-6 md:p-10 flex flex-col justify-center\">\n                <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n                  <span className=\"px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium rounded bg-primary/10 text-primary\">\n                    {featuredArticle.category}\n                  </span>\n                  <span className=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">\n                    {featuredArticle.readingTime} phút đọc\n                  </span>\n                </div>\n                <h3 className=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">\n                  {featuredArticle.title}\n                </h3>\n                <p className=\"text-muted-foreground mb-4 line-clamp-3\">\n                  {featuredArticle.excerpt}\n                </p>\n                <span className=\"inline-flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-primary\">\n                  Đọc tiếp <ArrowRight className=\"h-4 w-4 ml-1\" />\n                </span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </Link>\n        </section>\n      )}\n\n      {/* Categories */}\n      <section className=\"container\">\n        <div className=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-10\">\n          {CATEGORIES.map((cat) => (\n            <Link\n              key={cat.slug}\n              href={`/articles/category/${cat.slug}`}\n              className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-border hover:border-primary/50 hover:bg-primary/5 transition-all\"\n            >\n              <span className={`w-2 h-2 rounded-full ${cat.color}`} />\n              {cat.label}\n            </Link>\n          ))}\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      {/* Recent Posts */}\n      <section className=\"container py-12\">\n        <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-8\">\n          <h2 className=\"text-sm font-semibold text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wider\">\n\n[100 more lines in file. Use offset=81 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776590210947}}
{"type":"message","id":"298b9a30","parentId":"4ddbd3be","timestamp":"2026-04-19T09:16:57.675Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the full structure. Let me redesign the home page with:\n\n1. **Modern category pills** — gradient active state, better hover, all Vietnamese\n2. **Featured section** — larger, more dramatic with gradient overlay\n3. **Article cards** — modern glassmorphism cards with better hover effects\n4. **Better section headers** — with decorative lines\n5. **Modern newsletter section**\n6. **Better stats/metrics display**\n\nLet me also redesign the article card component and category navigation.Let me start with the home page redesign, then article cards.","thinkingSignature":"c99e48f89b44c50f9358de121f4a1003f5a0e3bdccdf87dacb9e27703585a5a4"},{"type":"text","text":"\n**Bước 1: Redesign ArticleCard:**\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1b84x58640zo_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/components/blog/article-card.tsx"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":867,"output":182,"cacheRead":141818,"cacheWrite":563,"totalTokens":143430,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776590210985,"responseId":"0633d084ec947cc7d62694d8c947f493"}}
{"type":"message","id":"fd1f497b","parentId":"298b9a30","timestamp":"2026-04-19T09:16:57.770Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_1b84x58640zo_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import Link from 'next/link'\nimport { Clock, Star } from 'lucide-react'\nimport { CATEGORIES } from '@/config/site'\n\nexport interface ArticleSummary {\n  slug: string\n  title: string\n  excerpt: string\n  category: string\n  tags: string[]\n  hero?: string | null\n  author: string\n  readingTime: number\n  publishedAt: string\n}\n\ninterface ArticleCardProps {\n  article: ArticleSummary\n  variant?: 'default' | 'compact'\n  featured?: boolean\n}\n\nexport function ArticleCard({ article, variant = 'default', featured = false }: ArticleCardProps) {\n  const cat = CATEGORIES.find((c) => c.slug === article.category)\n\n  if (variant === 'compact') {\n    return (\n      <Link\n        href={`/articles/${article.slug}`}\n        className=\"flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-accent transition-colors group\"\n      >\n        {article.hero && (\n          // eslint-disable-next-line @next/next/no-img-element\n          <img\n            src={article.hero}\n            alt={article.title}\n            className=\"w-16 h-16 rounded-md object-cover flex-shrink-0\"\n          />\n        )}\n        <div className=\"min-w-0\">\n          <p className=\"text-xs font-medium text-primary mb-1\">{cat?.label}</p>\n          <h3 className=\"text-sm font-medium line-clamp-2 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">\n            {article.title}\n          </h3>\n        </div>\n      </Link>\n    )\n  }\n\n  return (\n    <Link\n      href={`/articles/${article.slug}`}\n      className=\"group flex flex-col rounded-xl border border-border/40 overflow-hidden hover:border-primary/30 hover:shadow-md transition-all relative\"\n    >\n      {featured && (\n        <div className=\"absolute top-3 right-3 z-10\">\n          <span className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1 px-2 py-1 rounded-full bg-amber-500/90 text-white text-xs font-semibold shadow-sm\">\n            <Star className=\"h-3 w-3 fill-white\" />\n            Nổi bật\n          </span>\n        </div>\n      )}\n      {article.hero && (\n        // eslint-disable-next-line @next/next/no-img-element\n        <img\n          src={article.hero}\n          alt={article.title}\n          className=\"w-full h-44 object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500\"\n        />\n      )}\n      <div className=\"p-5 flex flex-col flex-1\">\n        <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n          {cat && (\n            <span\n              className={`px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium rounded ${cat.color} text-white`}\n            >\n              {cat.labelShort}\n            </span>\n          )}\n          <span className=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-xs text-muted-foreground\">\n            <Clock className=\"h-3 w-3\" />\n            {article.readingTime} phút\n          </span>\n        </div>\n\n        <h3 className=\"font-semibold mb-2 line-clamp-2 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">\n          {article.title}\n        </h3>\n        <p className=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground flex-1 line-clamp-3\">\n          {article.excerpt}\n        </p>\n\n        <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-border/40\">\n          <span className=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">{article.author}</span>\n          <span className=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">\n            {new Date(article.publishedAt).toLocaleDateString('vi-VN', {\n              day: 'numeric',\n              month: 'short',\n            })}\n          </span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </Link>\n  )\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776590217731}}
{"type":"message","id":"8f7c6ad7","parentId":"fd1f497b","timestamp":"2026-04-19T09:17:04.406Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me create a modern article card with:\n- Glassmorphism style\n- Gradient hover effects\n- Better typography\n- Category color indicators\n- Better shadows\n- Smooth animationsLet me also check the CATEGORIES config to understand the category system.","thinkingSignature":"0619cf077fa1c59fa9fb94059af631cf10f6b65226434516a57beeae647e2f9c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7gmm8zcm0d2d_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/config/site.ts"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":937,"output":100,"cacheRead":142102,"cacheWrite":1266,"totalTokens":144405,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776590217812,"responseId":"0633d08b9c385dea591be94e66febf57"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d780aae4","parentId":"8f7c6ad7","timestamp":"2026-04-19T09:17:04.455Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_7gmm8zcm0d2d_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"export const SITE = {\n  name: 'MAIY Tech Hub',\n  tagline: 'Học CNTT không bao giờ boring',\n  url: process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL || 'https://maiytechhub.com',\n  description:\n    'Nền tảng blog chia sẻ kiến thức CNTT chuẩn chỉnh: CTDL & Giải thuật, AI, Web Dev, DevOps. Kèm nhạc thư giãn và phòng học live.',\n  github: 'https://github.com/khuowgn/maiy-tech-hub',\n  author: 'MAIY Tech Hub',\n} as const\n\nexport const CATEGORIES = [\n  {\n    slug: 'ctdl',\n    label: 'CTDL & Giải thuật',\n    labelShort: 'CTDL',\n    description: 'Thuật toán, cấu trúc dữ liệu từ cơ bản đến nâng cao',\n    color: 'bg-blue-500',\n  },\n  {\n    slug: 'ai',\n    label: 'AI & Machine Learning',\n    labelShort: 'AI',\n    description: 'Trí tuệ nhân tạo, học máy, deep learning',\n    color: 'bg-purple-500',\n  },\n  {\n    slug: 'web-dev',\n    label: 'Web Development',\n    labelShort: 'Web Dev',\n    description: 'Frontend, backend, DevOps thực hành',\n    color: 'bg-green-500',\n  },\n  {\n    slug: 'devops',\n    label: 'DevOps',\n    labelShort: 'DevOps',\n    description: 'Docker, CI/CD, cloud, infrastructure',\n    color: 'bg-orange-500',\n  },\n  {\n    slug: 'cs-fundamentals',\n    label: 'CS Fundamentals',\n    labelShort: 'CS',\n    description: 'Nền tảng khoa học máy tính',\n    color: 'bg-red-500',\n  },\n] as const\n\nexport type CategorySlug = (typeof CATEGORIES)[number]['slug']\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776590224434}}
{"type":"message","id":"01ebe4fe","parentId":"d780aae4","timestamp":"2026-04-19T09:17:26.642Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me create a modern redesign. I'll focus on:1. **ArticleCard** — modern card with glassmorphism, gradient hover, better typography2. **Home page** — better section headers, modern layout\n3. **Category pills** — gradient active state, better hover4. **Featured section** — more dramatic with gradient overlay5. **Newsletter** — modern gradient design6. **Global CSS** — better design system with CSS variablesLet me start with the article card.","thinkingSignature":"3ddcb18d60ecf6341c03164383941a5eaf0bc15aaf844b15858c886f139affd8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3zzm9rbala2n_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/components/blog/article-card.tsx","content":"import Link from 'next/link'\nimport { Clock, ArrowRight, Star } from 'lucide-react'\nimport { CATEGORIES } from '@/config/site'\n\nexport interface ArticleSummary {\n  slug: string\n  title: string\n  excerpt: string\n  category: string\n  tags: string[]\n  hero?: string | null\n  author: string\n  readingTime: number\n  publishedAt: string\n}\n\ninterface ArticleCardProps {\n  article: ArticleSummary\n  variant?: 'default' | 'compact'\n  featured?: boolean\n  index?: number\n}\n\nexport function ArticleCard({ article, variant = 'default', featured = false, index = 0 }: ArticleCardProps) {\n  const cat = CATEGORIES.find((c) => c.slug === article.category)\n\n  if (variant === 'compact') {\n    return (\n      <Link\n        href={`/articles/${article.slug}`}\n        className=\"flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-muted/80 transition-all group border border-transparent hover:border-border\"\n      >\n        {article.hero && (\n          // eslint-disable-next-line @next/next/no-img-element\n          <img\n            src={article.hero}\n            alt={article.title}\n            className=\"w-16 h-16 rounded-lg object-cover flex-shrink-0\"\n          />\n        )}\n        <div className=\"min-w-0\">\n          {cat && (\n            <p className=\"text-xs font-semibold mb-1\" style={{ color: cat.color.replace('bg-', 'var(--cat-') + ')' }}>\n              {cat.labelShort}\n            </p>\n          )}\n          <h3 className=\"text-sm font-medium line-clamp-2 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">\n            {article.title}\n          </h3>\n        </div>\n      </Link>\n    )\n  }\n\n  // Gradient colors per category\n  const gradients: Record<string, string> = {\n    ctdl: 'from-blue-500/20 to-blue-600/5 hover:from-blue-500/30 hover:to-blue-600/10',\n    ai: 'from-violet-500/20 to-purple-600/5 hover:from-violet-500/30 hover:to-purple-600/10',\n    'web-dev': 'from-emerald-500/20 to-green-600/5 hover:from-emerald-500/30 hover:to-green-600/10',\n    devops: 'from-orange-500/20 to-amber-600/5 hover:from-orange-500/30 hover:to-amber-600/10',\n    'cs-fundamentals': 'from-red-500/20 to-rose-600/5 hover:from-red-500/30 hover:to-rose-600/10',\n  }\n\n  const gradient = gradients[article.category] || gradients['ctdl']\n\n  return (\n    <Link\n      href={`/articles/${article.slug}`}\n      className={`group flex flex-col rounded-2xl border border-border/60 bg-gradient-to-br ${gradient} overflow-hidden relative transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-black/10 hover:-translate-y-1`}\n    >\n      {/* Featured badge */}\n      {featured && (\n        <div className=\"absolute top-3 right-3 z-10\">\n          <span className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500 to-orange-500 text-white text-xs font-bold shadow-lg shadow-amber-500/30\">\n            <Star className=\"h-3 w-3 fill-white\" />\n            Nổi bật\n          </span>\n        </div>\n      )}\n\n      {/* Hero image */}\n      {article.hero ? (\n        <div className=\"relative h-48 overflow-hidden\">\n          {/* eslint-disable-next-line @next/next/no-img-element */}\n          <img\n            src={article.hero}\n            alt={article.title}\n            className=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700 ease-out\"\n          />\n          {/* Gradient overlay */}\n          <div className=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-background via-transparent to-transparent\" />\n        </div>\n      ) : (\n        <div className=\"h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/10 to-primary/5\" />\n      )}\n\n      {/* Content */}\n      <div className=\"p-5 flex flex-col flex-1 relative\">\n        {/* Category + Time */}\n        <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n          {cat && (\n            <span\n              className=\"px-2.5 py-1 text-[11px] font-bold rounded-md uppercase tracking-wide\"\n              style={{\n                backgroundColor: cat.color.replace('bg-', '') + '20',\n                color: cat.color.replace('bg-', '').replace('-500', '-400'),\n              }}\n            >\n              {cat.labelShort}\n            </span>\n          )}\n          <span className=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-xs text-muted-foreground\">\n            <Clock className=\"h-3 w-3\" />\n            {article.readingTime} phút\n          </span>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* Title */}\n        <h3 className=\"font-bold text-base md:text-lg mb-2 line-clamp-2 leading-snug group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">\n          {article.title}\n        </h3>\n\n        {/* Excerpt */}\n        <p className=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground flex-1 line-clamp-3 leading-relaxed\">\n          {article.excerpt}\n        </p>\n\n        {/* Footer */}\n        <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-border/40\">\n          <span className=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">{article.author}</span>\n          <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-medium text-primary/80 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">\n            Đọc ngay\n            <ArrowRight className=\"h-3 w-3 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\" />\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </Link>\n  )\n}\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":555,"output":1493,"cacheRead":143181,"cacheWrite":1162,"totalTokens":146391,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776590224474,"responseId":"0633d09267d1e09e43d060c5e14da501"}}
