{"type":"message","id":"fe214896","parentId":"4c520e10","timestamp":"2026-04-19T09:23:31.667Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"4254\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"6053576134\",\n  \"sender\": \"Khương Nịnh\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-04-19 09:23 UTC\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Khương Nịnh (6053576134)\",\n  \"id\": \"6053576134\",\n  \"name\": \"Khương Nịnh\",\n  \"username\": \"khuowgn\"\n}\n```\n\nkhá ok, tuy nhiên phần bài viết mới nhất hiệu ứng chưa thực sự được ưng ý, cảm giác khả lệch lạc chưa được mượt, ngoài ra form liên hệ thì đang khá sơ sài, footer cũng khá sơ sài, tôi cần bạn làm hiện đại hơn, mượt mà hơn (ưu tiên trải nghiệm mượt mà như các apple tối ưu sản phầm trên điện thoại và mac os của họ)"}],"timestamp":1776590611627}}
{"type":"message","id":"9c79668d","parentId":"fe214896","timestamp":"2026-04-19T09:24:00.814Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Lead wants:\n1. Smoother card hover animations (like Apple - fluid, spring-based)\n2. Better contact form (currently minimal)\n3. Better footer (more modern)\n4. Mobile-first, Apple-style smooth experience\n\nLet me fix all three on the feat/redesign branch.","thinkingSignature":"eee19480b18af9a1f8d88d2748d005865e16597ae42398bff49bbc95a78aa019"},{"type":"text","text":"Đang ở branch `feat/redesign` — fix tiếp:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qnl6dqmeb6b3_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/components/blog/article-card.tsx","content":"import Link from 'next/link'\nimport { Clock, ArrowRight, Star } from 'lucide-react'\nimport { CATEGORIES } from '@/config/site'\n\nexport interface ArticleSummary {\n  slug: string\n  title: string\n  excerpt: string\n  category: string\n  tags: string[]\n  hero?: string | null\n  author: string\n  readingTime: number\n  publishedAt: string\n}\n\ninterface ArticleCardProps {\n  article: ArticleSummary\n  variant?: 'default' | 'compact'\n  featured?: boolean\n  index?: number\n}\n\n// Apple-style spring animation via CSS\nconst cardStyles = `\n  @keyframes card-hover {\n    0% { transform: translateY(0px) scale(1); }\n    100% { transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.01); }\n  }\n  @keyframes image-zoom {\n    0% { transform: scale(1); }\n    100% { transform: scale(1.08); }\n  }\n  @keyframes arrow-slide {\n    0% { transform: translateX(0); }\n    100% { transform: translateX(4px); }\n  }\n  .article-card {\n    will-change: transform, box-shadow;\n    transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94),\n                box-shadow 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94),\n                border-color 0.3s ease;\n  }\n  .article-card:hover {\n    animation: card-hover 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1) forwards;\n  }\n  .article-card-img {\n    transition: transform 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);\n  }\n  .article-card:hover .article-card-img {\n    animation: image-zoom 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94) forwards;\n  }\n  .article-card-arrow {\n    transition: transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1), color 0.3s ease;\n  }\n  .article-card:hover .article-card-arrow {\n    animation: arrow-slide 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1) forwards;\n  }\n`\n\nexport function ArticleCard({ article, variant = 'default', featured = false, index = 0 }: ArticleCardProps) {\n  const cat = CATEGORIES.find((c) => c.slug === article.category)\n\n  if (variant === 'compact') {\n    return (\n      <Link\n        href={`/articles/${article.slug}`}\n        className=\"article-card flex items-start gap-3 p-3 rounded-xl border border-transparent hover:border-border hover:bg-muted/50 transition-all duration-300 group\"\n      >\n        {article.hero && (\n          // eslint-disable-next-line @next/next/no-img-element\n          <img\n            src={article.hero}\n            alt={article.title}\n            className=\"article-card-img w-16 h-16 rounded-xl object-cover flex-shrink-0\"\n          />\n        )}\n        <div className=\"min-w-0\">\n          {cat && (\n            <p className=\"text-xs font-semibold mb-1\" style={{ color: cat.color.replace('bg-', '') }}>\n              {cat.labelShort}\n            </p>\n          )}\n          <h3 className=\"text-sm font-medium line-clamp-2 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-200\">\n            {article.title}\n          </h3>\n        </div>\n      </Link>\n    )\n  }\n\n  const gradients: Record<string, string> = {\n    ctdl: 'hover:border-blue-400/60',\n    ai: 'hover:border-violet-400/60',\n    'web-dev': 'hover:border-emerald-400/60',\n    devops: 'hover:border-orange-400/60',\n    'cs-fundamentals': 'hover:border-red-400/60',\n  }\n\n  const glowColors: Record<string, string> = {\n    ctdl: 'shadow-blue-500/10',\n    ai: 'shadow-violet-500/10',\n    'web-dev': 'shadow-emerald-500/10',\n    devops: 'shadow-orange-500/10',\n    'cs-fundamentals': 'shadow-red-500/10',\n  }\n\n  const g = gradients[article.category] || gradients['ctdl']\n  const glow = glowColors[article.category] || glowColors['ctdl']\n\n  return (\n    <>\n      <style dangerouslySetInnerHTML={{ __html: cardStyles }} />\n      <Link\n        href={`/articles/${article.slug}`}\n        className={`article-card flex flex-col rounded-2xl border border-border/60 bg-background overflow-hidden relative group`}\n      >\n        {/* Featured badge */}\n        {featured && (\n          <div className=\"absolute top-3 right-3 z-20\">\n            <span className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-500 to-orange-500 text-white text-xs font-bold shadow-lg shadow-amber-500/25\">\n              <Star className=\"h-3 w-3 fill-white\" />\n              Nổi bật\n            </span>\n          </div>\n        )}\n\n        {/* Hero image */}\n        {article.hero ? (\n          <div className=\"relative overflow-hidden\" style={{ height: '200px' }}>\n            {/* eslint-disable-next-line @next/next/no-img-element */}\n            <img\n              src={article.hero}\n              alt={article.title}\n              className=\"article-card-img w-full h-full object-cover\"\n            />\n            {/* Frosted gradient overlay */}\n            <div className=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-background via-background/20 to-transparent\" />\n          </div>\n        ) : (\n          <div\n            className=\"h-40 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/10 to-primary/5\"\n            style={cat ? { background: `linear-gradient(135deg, ${cat.color.replace('bg-', '')}15, ${cat.color.replace('bg-', '')}05)` } : {}}\n          />\n        )}\n\n        {/* Content */}\n        <div className=\"p-5 flex flex-col flex-1 relative\">\n          {/* Category + time */}\n          <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\">\n            {cat && (\n              <span\n                className=\"px-2.5 py-1 text-[10px] font-bold rounded-md uppercase tracking-wider\"\n                style={{\n                  backgroundColor: cat.color.replace('bg-', '') + '18',\n                  color: cat.color.replace('bg-', '').replace('-500', '-400'),\n                }}\n              >\n                {cat.labelShort}\n              </span>\n            )}\n            <span className=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-xs text-muted-foreground\">\n              <Clock className=\"h-3 w-3\" />\n              {article.readingTime} phút\n            </span>\n          </div>\n\n          {/* Title */}\n          <h3 className=\"font-bold text-base leading-snug mb-2 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300 line-clamp-2\">\n            {article.title}\n          </h3>\n\n          {/* Excerpt */}\n          <p className=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground flex-1 line-clamp-3 leading-relaxed\">\n            {article.excerpt}\n          </p>\n\n          {/* Footer */}\n          <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-border/40\">\n            <span className=\"text-xs text-muted-foreground\">{article.author}</span>\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-semibold text-primary/80 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300\">\n              Đọc ngay\n              <ArrowRight className=\"article-card-arrow h-3.5 w-3.5\" />\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </Link>\n    </>\n  )\n}\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":338,"output":1933,"cacheRead":18358,"cacheWrite":132569,"totalTokens":153198,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776590611671,"responseId":"0633d2159d7d9000142db6a2ea72c6a5"}}
